title: Black Market Brawl - Caz's Cooky Quest through Curious Characters Convinced in Killing her Quickly
description: Caz Turner! The very same from that war about the planet exploding or something? Oh I can't remember, either way she returns to fight her way through a black market housed to many oddities and weirdos in an attempt to find her way back home! The Butcher, a titanous being of combat has issued the call, and so The Din falls to dissaray with the promises of a sword of wishes at the end of this bloodied path. Will Caz find herself drenched on the other side? You'll have to see...
author: Sal.TheSalty
